Snackvivor S2: Sushitopia - dicey-bot-battlezone

Snackvivor S2: Sushitopia
Spec Zone / dicey-bot-battlezone
Original message was deleted or could not be loaded.
the-dice-master BOT 04/02/2023 7:16 PM
This bot emulates the game Dicey Dungeons but with far less cards, far less rules and is multiplayer only! You can setup decks and play matches where you will go head to head with your opponent using randomly drawn dice to play cards that will affect yourself or your opponent. Each turn you draw four dice which you can use to activate the six cards you have selected prior to starting the game. If you are the first player, on your first turn you will only roll two dice! It does not matter what slot you set the cards to - You need specific dice to activate certain cards but what slot you set the card to is irrelevant! To add yourself to the player roster, type !create-player <@UserRole> - For example: !create-player @Fish To get the list of available cards you can choose from, type !list-cards To select which cards you will use for your battle, type !set-card <cardSlot> <cardName> - For example: !set-card 1 sword-slash Once your cards are all selected you can view your loadout with !loadout To start a game type !start-game <@UserRole1> <@UserRole@>! For example !start-game @Fish @Sappho On your turn you will be randomly given four dice, and you can play your dice on a card you have slotted by typing !play <cardName> <diceNumber> - For example: !play sword-slash 3 You start the game with 30 health. Some cards allow you to regain health but you cannot gain health over 30! Once you are ready to end your turn, type !end-turn If the game is over after a player types !end-turn, the game will end and the winner will be declared! The game has a maximum of 30 turns, if the game is not over before 30 turns the player with the highest health value come turn 30 will win. If they have tied health it will go into overtime where the game will end the next turn where a player's health is lower than anothers.

the-dice-master BOT 04/03/2023 6:25 PM
Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal [ ] damage to your opponent and freeze 1 die. 1 - 3 value only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 1 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!

the-dice-master BOT 04/04/2023 11:23 AM
Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal [ ] damage to your opponent and freeze 1 die. 1 - 3 value only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 1 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!

Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! Only deals 1 damamge if the dice value used was a 1! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot split an already split die! Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal [ ] damage to your opponent and freeze 1 die. 1 - 3 value only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 1 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!

Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! Only deals 1 damamge if the dice value used was a 1! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot split an already split die! Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal 2 damage to your opponent and freeze 1 random die. If the die is a 1 it only does 1 damage! 1 - 3 value dice only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 1 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!

the-dice-master BOT 04/04/2023 3:04 PM
Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! Only deals 1 damamge if the dice value used was a 1! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot split an already split die! Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal 2 damage to your opponent and freeze 1 random die. If the die is a 1 it only does 1 damage! 1 - 3 value dice only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 2 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!

the-dice-master BOT 04/04/2023 3:50 PM
Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! Only deals 1 damamge if the dice value used was a 1! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot split an already split die! Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! If you use a 1 valued die heal for 1 instead! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal 2 damage to your opponent and freeze 1 random die. If the die is a 1 it only does 1 damage! 1 - 3 value dice only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 2 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!

!rules
the-dice-master BOT 04/04/2023 11:48 PM
This bot emulates the game Dicey Dungeons but with far less cards, far less rules and is multiplayer only! You can setup decks and play matches where you will go head to head with your opponent using randomly drawn dice to play cards that will affect yourself or your opponent. Each turn you draw four dice which you can use to activate the six cards you have selected prior to starting the game. If you are the first player, on your first turn you will only roll two dice! It does not matter what slot you set the cards to - You need specific dice to activate certain cards but what slot you set the card to is irrelevant! To add yourself to the player roster, type !create-player <@UserRole> - For example: !create-player @Fish To get the list of available cards you can choose from, type !list-cards To select which cards you will use for your battle, type !set-card <cardSlot> <cardName> - For example: !set-card 1 sword-slash Once your cards are all selected you can view your loadout with !loadout To start a game type !start-game <@UserRole1> <@UserRole@>! For example !start-game @Fish @Sappho On your turn you will be randomly given four dice, and you can play your dice on a card you have slotted by typing !play <cardName> <diceNumber> - For example: !play sword-slash 3 You start the game with 30 health. Some cards allow you to regain health but you cannot gain health over 30! Once you are ready to end your turn, type !end-turn If the game is over after a player types !end-turn, the game will end and the winner will be declared! The game has a maximum of 30 turns, if the game is not over before 30 turns the player with the highest health value come turn 30 will win. If they have tied health it will go into overtime where the game will end the next turn where a player's health is lower than anothers.

!rules
the-dice-master BOT 04/06/2023 9:04 AM
This bot emulates the game Dicey Dungeons but with far less cards, far less rules and is multiplayer only! You can setup decks and play matches where you will go head to head with your opponent using randomly drawn dice to play cards that will affect yourself or your opponent. Each turn you draw four dice which you can use to activate the six cards you have selected prior to starting the game. If you are the first player, on your first turn you will only roll two dice! It does not matter what slot you set the cards to - You need specific dice to activate certain cards but what slot you set the card to is irrelevant! To add yourself to the player roster, type !create-player <@UserRole> - For example: !create-player @Fish To get the list of available cards you can choose from, type !list-cards To select which cards you will use for your battle, type !set-card <cardSlot> <cardName> - For example: !set-card 1 sword-slash Once your cards are all selected you can view your loadout with !loadout To start a game type !start-game <@UserRole1> <@UserRole@>! For example !start-game @Fish @Sappho On your turn you will be randomly given four dice, and you can play your dice on a card you have slotted by typing !play <cardName> <diceNumber> - For example: !play sword-slash 3 You start the game with 30 health. Some cards allow you to regain health but you cannot gain health over 30! Once you are ready to end your turn, type !end-turn If the game is over after a player types !end-turn, the game will end and the winner will be declared! The game has a maximum of 30 turns, if the game is not over before 30 turns the player with the highest health value come turn 30 will win. If they have tied health it will go into overtime where the game will end the next turn where a player's health is lower than anothers.

the-dice-master BOT 04/06/2023 9:05 AM
Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! Only deals 1 damage if the dice value used was a 1! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot split an already split die! Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! If you use a 1 valued die heal for 1 instead! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal 2 damage to your opponent and freeze 1 random die. If the die is a 1 it only does 1 damage! 1 - 3 value dice only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 2 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!

the-dice-master BOT 04/07/2023 1:36 AM
Here are the cards you can pick from: 1) sword-slash: Deal 2 damage to your opponent! Only deals 1 damage if the dice value used was a 1! 2) split: Take even dice and split it into two smaller dice. MUST BE EVEN. Cannot split an already split die! Cannot have double and split! 3) double: Take die and double it's value. 1 - 3 value only! Cannot have double and split! 4) fireball: Deal [ ] damage to opponent and burn 1 die. 1 or 2 dice value only! 5) first-aid-kit: Heal yourself for 2! If you use a 1 valued die heal for 1 instead! 6) ice-age: Freeze all of your opponents dice! Must be a 5! 7) blizzard: Deal 2 damage to your opponent and freeze 1 random die. If the die is a 1 it only does 1 damage! 1 - 3 value dice only! 8) dice-smash: Use one of your dice to destroy an opponets die! Must be a 3, 5 or 6! 9) present: Heals or damages a random player for a random amount. Good luck! 3, 4 or 5 dice value only! 10) life-drain: Deal 2 damage and heal yourself for 1. 5 - 6 value only! 11) cleanse: Remove burn from all dice and unblock all cards! Even dice values only! 12) static-shock: Deal 2 damage and randomly disable an opponents card for next round. 3 or 6 value only!
